WEBVTT

00:15.640 --> 00:16.480
Forget it.

00:17.710 --> 00:18.800
I won't wear it.

00:19.390 --> 00:20.030
Yes.

00:22.870 --> 00:24.390
What he remembers

00:25.160 --> 00:27.620
should be what I looked like
with black hair.

00:29.180 --> 00:31.750
Back then, I rarely wore hairpins.

00:32.750 --> 00:34.210
I thought they were tacky.

00:35.150 --> 00:35.940
Mi,

00:37.370 --> 00:38.860
am I really getting old?

00:41.110 --> 00:44.370
Do you think Shaoying will be disappointed
when he sees me?

00:44.750 --> 00:46.560
You are not old at all, Your Majesty.

00:46.560 --> 00:47.710
You are just as beautiful

00:47.710 --> 00:50.440
as when you sent
Young Master Shaoying off to war.

00:55.000 --> 00:55.750
Never mind.

00:57.470 --> 00:58.470
I'll put it on.

01:02.110 --> 01:03.640
It can cover up my gray hair.

01:04.640 --> 01:06.300
This will be our last meeting.

01:07.070 --> 01:09.320
I hope he'll remember me at my best.

01:10.950 --> 01:12.010
Yes, Your Majesty.

01:31.860 --> 01:33.940
Your Majesty, maybe we shouldn't go.

01:34.340 --> 01:37.870
You've been in so much pain
that you haven't slept well for days.

01:39.530 --> 01:40.979
I want to go and hear

01:42.060 --> 01:43.620
what the other life

01:44.580 --> 01:46.780
that little girl talked about was like.

01:49.979 --> 01:50.910
-Let's go.
-Yes.

02:04.340 --> 02:05.870
What is the meaning of this?

02:06.090 --> 02:07.060
The Eagle King has ordered

02:07.060 --> 02:09.460
us to protect the Empress Dowager tonight.

02:09.460 --> 02:10.259
Your Majesty,

02:10.570 --> 02:12.460
could His Highness already know

02:12.570 --> 02:14.700
that you are meeting Mr. Yuan tonight?

02:18.900 --> 02:20.220
We are here under the Eagle King's orders.

02:20.220 --> 02:22.530
Tonight, the Jiankang Palace
is welcoming Princess Pingning.

02:22.530 --> 02:24.060
Fearing that Southern Ye
might cause trouble,

02:24.060 --> 02:25.340
we were specifically ordered
to protect you.

02:25.340 --> 02:27.600
I am the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin.

02:27.620 --> 02:30.480
Do my words
carry less weight than the Eagle King's?

02:30.570 --> 02:31.460
Step aside!

02:33.460 --> 02:34.970
Are you trying to rebel?

02:35.060 --> 02:35.850
Hold on!

02:43.740 --> 02:44.900
Xie Huaigui?

02:46.410 --> 02:47.810
This is a state affair of Northern Qin.

02:47.810 --> 02:49.090
We will not tolerate outsiders
interfering.

02:49.090 --> 02:51.690
Please conduct yourself with dignity,
My Lord.

02:51.690 --> 02:53.940
You are now on the territory of Ye.

02:53.940 --> 02:56.070
Naturally, you must abide by our laws.

02:56.340 --> 02:59.620
Besides, the Empress Dowager
is an old friend of mine.

03:00.180 --> 03:02.250
I wish to invite her
for a chat today.

03:03.340 --> 03:05.780
And as the Grand Tutor of Ye,

03:06.410 --> 03:08.900
would I plot against the Empress Dowager?

03:12.500 --> 03:14.300
Please, Your Majesty.

04:42.159 --> 04:46.280
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

04:46.520 --> 04:49.270
[Episode 13]

04:52.500 --> 04:55.740
Grand Tutor, you didn't
break into Honglu Temple tonight

04:56.540 --> 04:57.810
just to get me

04:58.690 --> 05:00.250
out of this, did you?

05:01.330 --> 05:04.010
Is Hongyan Pavilion
in the Capital still there?

05:05.300 --> 05:06.810
It has now been renamed

05:08.010 --> 05:09.060
Lishui Pavilion.

05:10.250 --> 05:12.620
Twenty-five years ago,
the An and Lu families

05:12.620 --> 05:15.060
were executed at Hongyan Pavilion.

05:15.660 --> 05:16.860
You still can't let go

05:18.010 --> 05:20.010
of that ill-fated past, can you?

05:22.450 --> 05:23.660
Isn't what you're doing tonight

05:23.660 --> 05:25.010
also to put an end to that

05:25.010 --> 05:26.870
ill-fated past from 25 years ago?

05:28.540 --> 05:29.500
Everyone knows that back then,

05:29.500 --> 05:32.409
you and the youngest son of
the Right King of Virtue of Northern Qin,

05:32.409 --> 05:34.270
Mulian Ying, were deeply in love.

05:34.620 --> 05:37.180
But you were forced to marry into
the Northern Qin royal court.

05:37.180 --> 05:38.980
The Right King of Virtue
amassed military power and acted independently.

05:38.980 --> 05:42.240
He bribed the An and Lu families of Ye
with generous rewards

05:42.620 --> 05:46.210
and colluded with their armies
to fabricate military achievements.

05:46.210 --> 05:47.810
When the scheme was exposed,

05:48.659 --> 05:50.590
all these families were wiped out.

05:51.330 --> 05:54.890
The tragedy of the past is still vivid

05:55.770 --> 05:57.890
in my mind.

05:59.940 --> 06:03.660
I just want one word of truth from you.

06:05.010 --> 06:07.500
The case of the An and Lu families
back then—

06:09.810 --> 06:11.180
were they innocent?

06:12.250 --> 06:13.980
You're unwilling to accept it.

06:14.690 --> 06:16.060
I can understand.

06:17.210 --> 06:20.420
But back then, the An and Lu clans

06:20.860 --> 06:24.060
did collude with
our Right King of Virtue of Northern Qin.

06:24.890 --> 06:26.550
The evidence is irrefutable,

06:27.250 --> 06:28.710
and there was no frame-up.

06:34.740 --> 06:35.800
Stop the carriage!

06:37.890 --> 06:38.940
Grand Tutor Xie,

06:39.540 --> 06:41.400
we are both in our twilight years.

06:41.500 --> 06:44.360
The past should be left behind
like a flowing river.

06:45.250 --> 06:46.510
Those who should let go

06:47.100 --> 06:48.300
should let go.

07:00.770 --> 07:01.370
Master.

07:09.300 --> 07:11.370
Yaoyao asked me to tell you tonight

07:12.030 --> 07:15.210
that you must get the Empress Dowager
safely to Xiyue Restaurant.

07:15.210 --> 07:16.500
Now, only she

07:16.810 --> 07:18.250
can help you keep Lejun.

07:18.790 --> 07:20.990
[Xiyue Restaurant]

07:24.360 --> 07:27.270
[Closed]

07:36.620 --> 07:37.890
My Lady, bad news.

07:38.060 --> 07:40.330
The Eagle King has put
the entire Honglu Temple on high alert.

07:40.330 --> 07:41.790
No one is allowed in or out.

07:42.130 --> 07:45.260
Could the Eagle King
already know about tonight's plan?

07:47.250 --> 07:48.780
The Eagle King is ruthless.

07:49.330 --> 07:50.180
Once he's cornered,

07:50.180 --> 07:51.780
there's nothing he won't do.

07:52.010 --> 07:53.770
Especially since tonight's plan

07:53.770 --> 07:55.170
will ruin his grand plan.

07:56.180 --> 07:56.740
No.

07:56.890 --> 07:58.150
Shao Yang is in danger.

07:58.810 --> 07:59.810
I must go save her.

08:24.590 --> 08:28.010
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

08:28.310 --> 08:31.990
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

08:32.100 --> 08:36.460
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

08:36.820 --> 08:39.520
♪ So desolate ♪

08:40.100 --> 08:43.760
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

08:43.789 --> 08:47.330
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

08:47.520 --> 08:52.850
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

09:07.330 --> 09:07.940
Yaoyao.

09:08.380 --> 09:09.090
Mao.

09:10.140 --> 09:11.940
Why did you bring
the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin here?

09:11.940 --> 09:13.270
Did something go wrong?

09:14.940 --> 09:16.300
The auspicious hour has arrived.

09:16.300 --> 09:18.690
Please, Your Highness the Eagle King
and Princess Pingning,

09:18.690 --> 09:20.350
perform the ceremonial bows.

09:25.300 --> 09:27.210
Eagle King, please bow.

09:30.210 --> 09:32.020
Princess Pingning, please bow.

09:38.260 --> 09:40.380
Princess Pingning, please bow.

09:49.850 --> 09:50.570
Hold on!

09:56.810 --> 09:58.810
At the risk of my life,

09:59.060 --> 10:00.920
I oppose the political marriage!

10:02.260 --> 10:03.390
Here is my memorial.

10:03.850 --> 10:05.650
Please review it, Your Majesty!

10:10.330 --> 10:13.610
♪ Mother won't marry off her daughter ♪

10:13.610 --> 10:17.780
♪ The daughter is longing for her love ♪

10:20.180 --> 10:21.850
Step after step, I journey on;

10:22.610 --> 10:24.540
through a thousand miles of snow,
I return.

10:24.540 --> 10:26.540
We haven't seen each other in years.

10:26.920 --> 10:30.000
Shaoying, you've gone gray.

10:30.940 --> 10:32.490
I'm nearly fifty.

10:33.180 --> 10:35.900
Gray hair is hardly surprising.

10:44.210 --> 10:47.260
If you had made it back
on the day I was married,

10:48.090 --> 10:49.550
and we'd left together...

10:50.900 --> 10:53.350
how do you think things
would've turned out?

10:53.350 --> 10:54.140
Shao Yang...

11:00.330 --> 11:01.300
No one's...

11:03.210 --> 11:05.140
called me that in a very long time.

11:06.660 --> 11:07.380
Shao Yang.

11:09.210 --> 11:12.090
Back then, was it you

11:12.730 --> 11:14.730
who suggested that the late Emperor

11:17.140 --> 11:18.400
have my father killed?

11:47.060 --> 11:48.190
Is this cup of tea...

11:51.090 --> 11:52.970
poisoned too?

12:05.490 --> 12:07.950
Perhaps
the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin

12:08.020 --> 12:09.260
had her own reasons.

12:13.140 --> 12:15.090
Mao, if it were you,

12:15.900 --> 12:18.900
would you still want to see
this person you once loved?

12:25.330 --> 12:26.180
How...

12:27.570 --> 12:28.430
has Lejun been?

12:29.060 --> 12:30.020
Tonight is the night the Eagle King

12:30.020 --> 12:31.260
comes to wed Lejun.

12:31.970 --> 12:33.330
Aren't you going to see her off?

12:33.330 --> 12:34.690
I won't let Lejun leave.

12:34.810 --> 12:37.450
So you went to Cui Mansion?

12:38.900 --> 12:41.060
You asked Chief Clerk Cui
to contact the noble families

12:41.060 --> 12:43.660
to help Lejun reject the marriage,
didn't you?

12:47.020 --> 12:48.020
The foundation of Ye

12:48.020 --> 12:49.940
relies on the descendants
of the noble families.

12:49.940 --> 12:52.670
If we send Princess Pingning
to Northern Qin now—

12:52.780 --> 12:54.660
those Northern Qin people
are from a barbaric land.

12:54.660 --> 12:55.450
They are uncivilized

12:55.450 --> 12:56.570
and lack proper etiquette.

12:56.570 --> 12:58.450
Making a noble lady marry a barbarian

12:58.450 --> 13:00.330
is an insult to all noble families.

13:00.330 --> 13:02.610
Your Majesty,
have you forgotten the incident of Wenxi?

13:02.610 --> 13:05.180
In the past, the late Emperor
reduced the lands of the nobles,

13:05.180 --> 13:07.980
and internal strife
plunged the realm into chaos.

13:08.210 --> 13:09.490
Your Majesty, Empress Dowager,

13:09.490 --> 13:11.090
you must not repeat the same mistakes!

13:11.090 --> 13:14.330
Your Majesty, Empress Dowager,
we beg you to reconsider!

13:17.450 --> 13:19.250
Your Majesty, Empress Dowager.

13:19.490 --> 13:21.300
I do not want to marry into Northern Qin,

13:21.300 --> 13:23.020
nor do I want to disgrace Ye's prestige.

13:23.020 --> 13:25.900
I beg you to retract the order!

13:27.180 --> 13:28.940
If the political marriage fails today,

13:28.940 --> 13:30.540
the alliance will be voided.

13:30.900 --> 13:34.160
And the three prefectures
will return to our Northern Qin.

13:40.540 --> 13:42.450
In this puppet show,

13:44.020 --> 13:46.020
do none of us get a good ending?

13:48.090 --> 13:49.220
Jiayu doesn't know—

13:50.540 --> 13:51.940
you didn't want to see me.

13:56.300 --> 13:57.500
You wanted to kill me.

14:00.140 --> 14:01.140
I just want to know

14:03.100 --> 14:04.900
if you have let go of your hatred—

14:08.850 --> 14:10.210
your hatred for my son

14:11.420 --> 14:13.350
and the Northern Qin royal family.

14:16.900 --> 14:17.690
I have.

14:22.330 --> 14:23.210
You are lying.

14:25.420 --> 14:26.820
If you had truly let it go,

14:27.140 --> 14:30.200
why would you forge weapons
under Xiao Wuyi's command?

14:31.570 --> 14:34.540
All these years,
you've been helping the Beifu Army.

14:34.540 --> 14:36.070
You have hated us all along.

14:36.900 --> 14:39.420
You hate me, my son,

14:39.690 --> 14:41.380
and everyone in Northern Qin.

14:41.660 --> 14:43.060
If you had the chance
to overthrow Northern Qin,

14:43.060 --> 14:44.860
you wouldn't miss it, would you?

14:52.330 --> 14:53.060
So...

14:55.570 --> 14:56.940
before I die,

14:59.140 --> 15:00.900
I have to kill you.

15:07.690 --> 15:08.850
If I die,

15:10.450 --> 15:11.910
will you truly be at peace?

15:20.970 --> 15:21.690
Yes.

15:25.330 --> 15:25.970
Alright.

15:26.540 --> 15:27.330
My life...

15:30.420 --> 15:31.150
is yours now.

15:40.380 --> 15:42.020
Young Lord Xiao has arrived!

15:43.090 --> 15:44.420
Young Lord Xiao is here?

15:45.570 --> 15:46.610
Why is he here?

15:56.380 --> 15:57.240
Your Highness.

15:57.900 --> 16:00.700
This is an everlasting Ruyi lantern
I made myself.

16:01.940 --> 16:05.140
I'm presenting it to you
as a  celebration of your wedding.

16:08.180 --> 16:11.140
Greetings, Your Majesty, Empress Dowager.

16:12.210 --> 16:14.660
Since you came to congratulate,

16:15.300 --> 16:16.900
why did you wait until the auspicious hour

16:16.900 --> 16:18.760
almost passed to finally show up?

16:19.780 --> 16:20.660
Tonight

16:20.660 --> 16:23.140
is the wedding of the Eagle King
and Princess Pingning.

16:23.140 --> 16:25.420
All the people of Jiankang
lit lanterns to pray.

16:25.420 --> 16:26.850
Though it made my carriage
difficult to move,

16:26.850 --> 16:28.710
it shows the hearts of the people.

16:28.850 --> 16:31.210
Ye and Northern Qin have formed
an alliance through a political marriage,

16:31.210 --> 16:33.450
ceasing war, nourishing the people,
and reopening trade markets.

16:33.450 --> 16:35.490
There will be no more soldiers
shedding blood.

16:35.490 --> 16:39.210
This is truly a blessing
for all the people.

16:40.940 --> 16:42.600
You are wrong, Your Highness.

16:43.380 --> 16:45.940
Our noble families
have a century-old heritage.

16:45.940 --> 16:47.780
We are the pillars of Ye

16:47.780 --> 16:49.660
and the orthodox lineage of the world.

16:49.660 --> 16:51.090
Now, to form an alliance,

16:51.450 --> 16:52.850
we actually resorted
to a political marriage,

16:52.850 --> 16:55.380
groveling and flattering,
disgracing our national ethos.

16:55.380 --> 16:55.780
We absolutely cannot...

16:55.780 --> 16:56.580
Your Majesty.

16:57.450 --> 16:59.690
I also have a memorial to present today.

17:00.060 --> 17:00.810
Present it.

17:02.300 --> 17:04.230
During the severe flood last year,

17:05.660 --> 17:08.380
the Cui family, the Lu family of Fanyang,

17:08.380 --> 17:09.980
and the Wen family of Qinghe,

17:10.380 --> 17:12.290
under the guise of praying for the people,

17:12.290 --> 17:14.020
held a winding stream banquet.

17:14.180 --> 17:14.859
In reality,

17:15.490 --> 17:17.660
they took the opportunity
to seize the people's land.

17:17.660 --> 17:18.290
May I ask—

17:20.490 --> 17:23.250
is the dignity of the noble families
Chief Clerk Cui spoke of

17:23.250 --> 17:24.579
referring to this?

17:40.690 --> 17:41.580
Now,

17:42.290 --> 17:43.490
can you rest assured?

17:47.900 --> 17:48.820
Why?

17:49.690 --> 17:50.820
After so many years,

17:51.380 --> 17:52.940
don't you hate me?

17:53.770 --> 17:56.140
I know you were the one
who advised the late Emperor

17:56.140 --> 17:57.450
to kill my father.

17:58.770 --> 17:59.580
I also know

18:00.200 --> 18:03.090
that you
were already pregnant at that time.

18:04.660 --> 18:06.770
You were no longer just my Shao Yang.

18:10.420 --> 18:11.290
Rest assured!

18:11.380 --> 18:12.710
Yuan Xiaoliu won't die!

18:17.490 --> 18:19.750
I have already swapped the poisoned tea.

18:20.100 --> 18:21.690
Actually, I knew that the Empress Dowager

18:21.690 --> 18:23.150
came to tonight's meeting

18:23.450 --> 18:24.530
in the name of love,

18:25.290 --> 18:27.610
but in truth, she came for your life.

18:28.260 --> 18:30.520
But Your Majesty, I also wanted you to see

18:31.330 --> 18:33.660
the lingering affection between you two.

18:33.820 --> 18:35.420
Yuan Xiaoliu could have left,

18:35.420 --> 18:37.480
but he wanted to see you one last time.

18:37.690 --> 18:38.550
There's no need

18:38.890 --> 18:40.920
for you two to fight to the death.

18:43.860 --> 18:45.250
I can spare your life,

18:46.260 --> 18:47.740
but I need a promise.

18:50.970 --> 18:52.210
As long as you live,

18:52.940 --> 18:55.700
you must never set foot in Northern Qin.

18:58.290 --> 18:59.050
I promise.

19:00.520 --> 19:01.720
I will give the order.

19:02.050 --> 19:05.450
Northern Qin won't send anyone
to hunt you down anymore.

19:06.340 --> 19:07.450
From now on,

19:08.690 --> 19:10.170
you can live freely.

19:17.250 --> 19:17.920
Watch out!

19:22.810 --> 19:23.330
Yaoyao!

19:25.530 --> 19:26.730
It's Mulian Yu's men.

19:27.180 --> 19:28.620
He wants me dead.

19:29.510 --> 19:30.770
If I die in Southern Ye,

19:31.820 --> 19:33.550
the peace talks will be ruined.

19:35.860 --> 19:36.490
Shao Yang!

19:40.770 --> 19:41.500
Come with me!

19:47.290 --> 19:48.690
Shao Yang, hang in there!

19:48.860 --> 19:50.260
I will get you out safely!

19:56.690 --> 19:58.620
Your Highness, we can continue.

20:01.420 --> 20:03.550
Your Highness, to achieve your goals,

20:03.940 --> 20:05.740
you really do whatever it takes.

20:07.620 --> 20:09.180
Princess Pingning is not only

20:09.180 --> 20:10.910
the sister of your best friend,

20:11.010 --> 20:13.870
but also like a sister
to your secondary concubine.

20:13.940 --> 20:16.140
Don't you have any mercy?

20:16.860 --> 20:19.660
You keep saying it's for the people
of Southern Ye,

20:19.660 --> 20:20.970
but it's just for your own

20:20.970 --> 20:22.380
lust for power and ambition.

20:22.380 --> 20:23.820
So what?

20:24.620 --> 20:25.820
For the Beifu Reform

20:25.970 --> 20:27.500
and to reclaim the Capital,

20:27.500 --> 20:28.830
I can sacrifice anyone.

20:29.860 --> 20:32.460
So, Your Highness,
you have no choice tonight.

20:32.710 --> 20:34.800
This pact must be signed.

20:35.770 --> 20:37.140
What if I don't?

20:40.580 --> 20:41.450
Bad news!

20:42.660 --> 20:45.060
There's been a murder at Xiyue Restaurant!

20:45.140 --> 20:46.380
It's just a place of entertainment.

20:46.380 --> 20:47.580
What's to panic about?

20:47.580 --> 20:50.440
The Empress Dowager of Northern Qin
was also there!

20:57.250 --> 20:58.380
Did you think

20:58.490 --> 21:01.020
I would only send people
to kill Yuan Xiaoliu?

21:01.490 --> 21:03.100
Having fought with you for years,

21:03.100 --> 21:05.430
I naturally knew you'd have a backup plan.

21:06.010 --> 21:08.740
So I had people
ambush outside Xiyue Restaurant.

21:09.210 --> 21:10.900
If Xie Jiayu really managed to resolve

21:10.900 --> 21:12.970
the grudge between Yuan Xiaoliu
and the Empress Dowager,

21:12.970 --> 21:15.690
then I might as well
kill the Empress Dowager too.

21:15.690 --> 21:19.100
If the dignified Empress Dowager
of Northern Qin dies in Southern Ye,

21:19.100 --> 21:21.180
what will the situation be?

21:23.580 --> 21:26.620
Since Southern Ye broke the alliance
and the marriage agreement first,

21:26.620 --> 21:29.350
then sent assassins
to kill our Empress Dowager,

21:29.450 --> 21:31.620
-and...
-Prince Qi has arrived!

21:55.970 --> 21:57.170
Qing Long and Yan Yue?

21:57.190 --> 21:58.080
It's Xiao Wuyi.

21:59.140 --> 21:59.940
He knew long ago

21:59.940 --> 22:02.580
that I brought Yuan Xiaoliu to see
the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin.

22:02.580 --> 22:03.210
Let's go!

22:21.500 --> 22:22.760
Eagle King, Mulian Yu,

22:22.860 --> 22:26.120
receive the decree of the Empress Dowager
of Northern Qin.

22:29.210 --> 22:31.540
Eagle King Mulian Yu, receive the decree!

22:35.950 --> 22:38.100
Since you entered Ye
holding the tally of Northern Qin,

22:38.100 --> 22:40.180
you should follow the etiquette
of the world.

22:40.180 --> 22:43.100
Canceling the marriage agreement
with Princess Pingning

22:43.100 --> 22:44.660
and restoring the peace agreement

22:44.660 --> 22:47.340
is an act that follows the will
of heaven and the people.

22:47.340 --> 22:48.940
You're ordered
to sign the peace agreement immediately

22:48.940 --> 22:51.100
and return
the three prefectures to Southern Ye.

22:51.100 --> 22:51.900
Thus decreed.

22:53.340 --> 22:53.930
No.

22:54.580 --> 22:56.730
Xiyue Restaurant
is in a sea of fire right now.

22:56.730 --> 22:57.420
Our Empress Dowager...

22:57.420 --> 22:59.020
Your Empress Dowager has now

22:59.100 --> 23:01.300
returned safely to Honglu Temple.

23:01.770 --> 23:03.230
And she asked me to tell you

23:03.250 --> 23:04.780
that she has long been aware

23:04.820 --> 23:06.340
of your actions tonight.

23:06.940 --> 23:07.770
Impossible.

23:08.010 --> 23:08.860
Impossible?

23:09.050 --> 23:11.690
You can ask Young Lord Xiao about this.

23:35.340 --> 23:36.010
Lejun.

23:37.660 --> 23:38.720
It's all right now.

23:43.420 --> 23:43.940
Wuyi.

23:44.420 --> 23:45.380
Although I said

23:45.490 --> 23:47.340
I couldn't hide behind you all the time,

23:47.340 --> 23:48.660
for what happened tonight,

23:48.660 --> 23:50.060
I still want to thank you.

23:50.770 --> 23:51.830
No need to thank me.

23:52.250 --> 23:53.780
You should thank Xie Jiayu.

23:54.580 --> 23:56.250
I originally wanted
to watch from the sidelines,

23:56.250 --> 23:58.140
but she didn't give up
time and time again.

23:58.140 --> 23:59.660
I couldn't help but admire her.

23:59.660 --> 24:01.720
So I placed spies in Xiyue Restaurant

24:01.860 --> 24:03.390
to ensure absolute safety.

24:05.580 --> 24:06.640
Where is Xie Jiayu?

24:08.820 --> 24:10.880
She was injured in Xiyue Restaurant.

24:18.660 --> 24:20.730
Your Highness, please wait.

24:25.290 --> 24:27.820
Your Highness,
are you going back on your word?

24:27.820 --> 24:29.860
The one who just promised
to cancel the political marriage

24:29.860 --> 24:31.260
is your Empress Dowager.

24:31.340 --> 24:33.180
I always keep my word

24:33.510 --> 24:34.770
and never go back on it.

24:35.660 --> 24:37.190
Then what do you want to say?

24:37.340 --> 24:38.600
On the day of the match,

24:38.630 --> 24:39.760
I took a fancy to you.

24:40.730 --> 24:42.860
Wanting to marry you
was my selfish desire,

24:42.860 --> 24:43.900
but not a pretense.

24:43.900 --> 24:46.420
Don't talk nonsense. Shut up.

24:46.490 --> 24:48.380
This is our custom in Northern Qin.

24:48.380 --> 24:49.510
If you want someone,

24:49.730 --> 24:50.860
you shout it out loud

24:51.010 --> 24:52.410
so that heaven will know.

24:52.420 --> 24:53.210
Li Lejun,

24:54.290 --> 24:55.420
with or without the political marriage,

24:55.420 --> 24:56.480
I want to marry you.

24:57.050 --> 24:58.250
If you are unwilling,

24:58.650 --> 24:59.650
I won't force you.

25:03.580 --> 25:05.490
If you change your mind one day,

25:05.660 --> 25:07.100
come to Northern Qin to find me.

25:07.100 --> 25:08.430
My Eagle King's Mansion

25:08.520 --> 25:10.450
will always open its doors for you!

25:51.770 --> 25:53.590
How is your injury?

25:56.140 --> 25:56.690
I'm fine.

25:57.290 --> 25:58.290
Ruisheng used

25:58.290 --> 25:59.450
the finest wound ointment on me.

25:59.450 --> 26:01.050
It won't leave a single scar.

26:10.450 --> 26:11.980
It seems to have succeeded.

26:21.140 --> 26:22.270
Thank you for today.

26:23.180 --> 26:23.970
Why thank me?

26:24.420 --> 26:26.780
You saved the life
of the Northern Qin Empress Dowager.

26:26.780 --> 26:28.420
If anything had happened to her
in Jiankang,

26:28.420 --> 26:29.940
the consequences
would have been unimaginable.

26:29.940 --> 26:31.400
Actually, I was just lucky

26:31.530 --> 26:32.390
and won the bet.

26:33.690 --> 26:35.750
But if you don't want to do something,

26:35.770 --> 26:37.100
no one can make you do it.

26:37.770 --> 26:39.660
You knew early on
that I took Yuan Xiaoliu,

26:39.660 --> 26:42.250
so you had Qing Long and Yan Yue
guard outside Xiyue Restaurant,

26:42.250 --> 26:43.050
didn't you?

26:45.100 --> 26:47.140
But if it weren't
for your repeated insistence,

26:47.140 --> 26:48.800
things wouldn't be like this.

26:49.210 --> 26:50.730
The Northern Qin Empress Dowager

26:50.730 --> 26:52.390
has agreed to the peace terms.

26:55.380 --> 26:57.340
Later, the Northern Qin Empress Dowager
told me

26:57.340 --> 26:58.450
that she didn't want
the Eagle King to gain the support

26:58.450 --> 27:00.620
of the Southern Ye royal family
in the first place.

27:00.620 --> 27:02.250
She just wanted to see Yuan Xiaoliu.

27:02.250 --> 27:03.980
That's why she made this trade.

27:04.530 --> 27:07.050
Do you think Yuan Xiaoliu and she

27:07.100 --> 27:08.630
really let go of each other?

27:12.660 --> 27:13.460
What's wrong?

27:14.380 --> 27:15.180
Yizhi...

27:18.100 --> 27:19.030
wants to see you.

27:24.730 --> 27:25.590
-Yaoyao.
-Mao.

27:26.820 --> 27:27.880
How's your injury?

27:28.180 --> 27:29.240
Does it hurt badly?

27:30.250 --> 27:32.110
I'm fine. It's just a flesh wound.

27:34.140 --> 27:36.820
Lejun's marriage agreement
has finally been canceled.

27:36.820 --> 27:37.860
You two siblings

27:38.340 --> 27:40.340
don't have to be separated anymore.

27:40.970 --> 27:42.530
When I leave Jiankang with you,

27:42.530 --> 27:44.460
I'll figure something out for her.

27:47.530 --> 27:48.240
Mao.

27:49.720 --> 27:50.980
I know you won't leave.

27:53.180 --> 27:54.180
I also know

27:54.660 --> 27:57.190
you're about to marry a girl
of the Cui family.

27:57.210 --> 27:59.010
Although neither of you told me,

27:59.450 --> 28:00.860
I already knew

28:01.770 --> 28:03.570
when you went to the Cui Mansion.

28:04.250 --> 28:04.900
Yaoyao.

28:07.770 --> 28:08.570
Do you hate me?

28:10.420 --> 28:11.580
Why would I hate you?

28:14.250 --> 28:15.450
Sometimes I wonder

28:16.940 --> 28:19.200
if it's because I was too childish before

28:19.860 --> 28:21.730
that neither you nor Xiao Wuyi

28:22.050 --> 28:23.850
was willing to tell me the truth.

28:24.450 --> 28:25.900
I was a bit angry at first.

28:27.050 --> 28:28.450
You have such ambitions,

28:28.820 --> 28:30.550
but why didn't you ever tell me?

28:33.820 --> 28:34.950
But later I thought,

28:36.250 --> 28:38.290
it was always me wanting to do something

28:38.290 --> 28:40.150
and dragging you to accompany me.

28:42.100 --> 28:43.970
But I didn't know what you wanted.

28:44.900 --> 28:45.580
Actually,

28:47.480 --> 28:49.140
I never truly understood you.

28:49.940 --> 28:51.000
It's not like that.

28:52.010 --> 28:53.610
I just wanted to protect you.

28:53.940 --> 28:54.940
I hope you will live easily and happily

28:54.940 --> 28:56.290
for your whole life,

28:56.530 --> 28:57.690
and never see this world's

28:57.690 --> 28:58.660
cruel side.

29:02.290 --> 29:02.900
Yaoyao.

29:06.530 --> 29:08.380
Are you willing to enter the palace?

29:08.380 --> 29:09.530
Are you asking me to be your consort?

29:09.530 --> 29:10.660
I mean in the future.

29:11.530 --> 29:12.250
One day,

29:12.420 --> 29:13.750
I will truly hold power.

29:13.860 --> 29:15.010
At that time, there will be no He family

29:15.010 --> 29:15.770
or Cui family.

29:15.770 --> 29:16.970
There will only be us.

29:18.340 --> 29:18.970
I think

29:19.770 --> 29:21.570
you can divorce Xiao Wuyi first.

29:22.180 --> 29:23.970
Do you know there is
a Bureau of Devices in the palace?

29:23.970 --> 29:25.530
You can be a female official there.

29:25.530 --> 29:27.180
Don't you like mechanical devices?

29:27.180 --> 29:27.970
How could the craftsmanship
outside the palace

29:27.970 --> 29:29.370
be as good as that inside?

29:29.450 --> 29:30.580
But I don't like it.

29:39.470 --> 29:40.190
Mao.

29:41.690 --> 29:43.550
This is not the path I want to take.

29:45.940 --> 29:47.050
I have grown up.

29:48.820 --> 29:51.760
Between cruel truths and false illusions,

29:52.490 --> 29:53.490
I want the former.

29:56.490 --> 29:57.490
You just chose

29:58.250 --> 30:00.310
what you thought was more important.

30:00.320 --> 30:02.120
So you don't need to feel guilty,

30:02.530 --> 30:04.330
nor do you need to worry about me.

30:14.690 --> 30:16.150
So you still want to leave?

30:19.730 --> 30:21.210
But you have never left Jiankang,

30:21.210 --> 30:22.420
and you will be all alone...

30:22.420 --> 30:23.950
The road is beneath my feet.

30:24.450 --> 30:25.650
Only by traveling far

30:26.490 --> 30:28.820
will I know where my home is.

30:42.420 --> 30:43.750
It seems that right now,

30:45.900 --> 30:47.430
I still can't keep you here.

31:09.250 --> 31:10.510
You should be grateful

31:11.010 --> 31:12.070
that you survived.

31:12.940 --> 31:14.400
Phoenix Bone Poison Pill.

31:16.800 --> 31:20.000
Actually, today, it wasn't just her
who wanted to kill me;

31:21.050 --> 31:22.450
I also wanted to kill her.

31:22.810 --> 31:24.270
It was Jiayu's appearance

31:27.140 --> 31:28.540
that finally stopped me.

31:32.730 --> 31:33.730
What a waste.

31:37.530 --> 31:38.730
This girl Jiayu

31:39.860 --> 31:42.420
is always so drawn to the light

31:44.340 --> 31:45.530
and so passionate that the dark

31:45.530 --> 31:46.940
in one's heart

31:47.010 --> 31:48.140
has nowhere to hide.

31:49.530 --> 31:52.330
It makes me reluctant
to be too cruel to this world.

32:00.100 --> 32:01.530
Is this also the reason

32:02.290 --> 32:03.490
why you fell for her?

32:12.210 --> 32:14.470
The last time I saw you drinking like this

32:15.100 --> 32:16.580
was at Jiuzhang Plain,

32:17.340 --> 32:18.740
when there was no way out.

32:27.010 --> 32:28.540
Now that she's not leaving,

32:28.940 --> 32:31.010
is it possible for the two of you to...

32:31.010 --> 32:32.540
I don't have much time left.

32:34.530 --> 32:35.450
Xie Jiayu...

32:38.050 --> 32:40.250
Xie Jiayu was never my responsibility.

32:40.620 --> 32:42.550
And I have never expected her to be.

32:43.690 --> 32:44.890
I promised her mother

32:45.770 --> 32:47.370
not to involve her in danger.

32:49.100 --> 32:50.450
Haven't I told you?

32:51.450 --> 32:52.940
I read the fortune for you two.

32:52.940 --> 32:55.380
Your destiny with her
definitely won't just end here.

32:55.380 --> 32:56.290
You two are...

32:56.290 --> 32:57.890
I never believed in destiny.

32:59.620 --> 33:00.490
If what destiny leaves for me

33:00.490 --> 33:02.050
never belonged to me in the first place,

33:02.050 --> 33:03.250
I will personally...

33:03.340 --> 33:04.140
What?

33:09.010 --> 33:09.860
Cut it off.

33:15.690 --> 33:16.490
Cut it off?

33:37.380 --> 33:38.110
You're back?

33:40.050 --> 33:41.780
Why haven't you gone to bed yet?

33:42.210 --> 33:42.900
Tonight...

33:46.440 --> 33:48.170
the moonlight is quite pretty.

33:56.530 --> 33:57.530
Have you...

33:58.940 --> 34:00.340
talked it out with Yizhi?

34:06.140 --> 34:07.800
Maybe ordinary people like us

34:08.050 --> 34:09.790
and people with lofty ambitions like you

34:09.790 --> 34:11.920
were never meant to walk the same path.

34:23.780 --> 34:25.310
Not having great ambitions

34:26.050 --> 34:27.909
doesn't mean having no backbone.

34:28.780 --> 34:29.380
Xie Jiayu,

34:31.820 --> 34:33.280
you're a very good person.

34:41.090 --> 34:43.750
I have decided
to take Yuan Xiaoliu as my master.

34:43.949 --> 34:44.840
From now on,

34:44.860 --> 34:47.699
I will follow him to improve my skills
in mechanics and construction.

34:47.699 --> 34:48.960
I will leave Jiankang.

34:49.530 --> 34:51.969
Maybe I will follow him to your Beifu.

34:57.010 --> 34:57.780
Xiao Wuyi.

34:58.050 --> 34:59.010
Yuan Xiaoliu's Cangfeng Forge

34:59.010 --> 35:00.170
works really well for me.

35:00.170 --> 35:01.860
Can you ask him
to share half of it with me?

35:01.860 --> 35:04.700
Who told you that Cangfeng Forge
belongs to Yuan Xiaoliu?

35:04.700 --> 35:05.630
Whose is it then?

35:07.220 --> 35:07.900
It's mine.

35:08.530 --> 35:09.610
Then can you share half

35:09.610 --> 35:10.900
of your Cangfeng Forge with me?

35:10.900 --> 35:12.300
Anyway,
after you go to the Northern Border,

35:12.300 --> 35:13.700
you won't use it anymore.

35:15.700 --> 35:16.860
Let me think about it.

35:16.860 --> 35:18.320
You need to think about it?

35:22.970 --> 35:24.430
Why can't I think about it?

35:25.010 --> 35:26.050
Even if I'm not at home,

35:26.050 --> 35:27.380
this home is still mine.

35:28.050 --> 35:29.900
With such a petty personality,

35:29.970 --> 35:31.900
no wonder you can't find yourself a girl.

35:31.900 --> 35:33.700
I already have 3 concubines in my mansion,

35:33.700 --> 35:35.500
which is annoying enough for me.

35:36.380 --> 35:37.380
Do the three of us

35:37.380 --> 35:38.980
have anything to do with you?

35:39.410 --> 35:40.780
If you keep acting like this,

35:40.780 --> 35:42.240
you'll be single forever.

35:42.820 --> 35:44.010
In case you die in the future,

35:44.010 --> 35:45.260
no one will collect your body.

35:45.260 --> 35:46.340
Taking heaven and earth as one's grave

35:46.340 --> 35:47.670
is also a kind of beauty.

35:48.090 --> 35:49.350
I don't need a partner.

35:51.220 --> 35:53.420
And I definitely don't need a weakness.

35:55.380 --> 35:57.980
I don't believe
you don't have anyone you like.

36:01.570 --> 36:02.530
No, no, no.

36:02.700 --> 36:03.490
That look in your eyes—

36:03.490 --> 36:05.050
you definitely have someone you like.

36:05.050 --> 36:05.820
What does she look like?

36:05.820 --> 36:06.820
Tell me about her.

36:06.980 --> 36:08.710
What does it have to do with you?

36:09.050 --> 36:10.010
Just gossiping.

36:10.170 --> 36:13.770
It's precisely because it has
nothing to do with me that I can ask.

36:24.780 --> 36:26.180
Why are you staring at me?

36:28.450 --> 36:29.380
Anyway...

36:30.970 --> 36:32.300
she is prettier than you

36:32.610 --> 36:33.900
and more sensible than you.

36:33.900 --> 36:35.610
She's better than you in everything.

36:35.610 --> 36:36.420
Impossible.

36:36.940 --> 36:37.820
In this world,

36:37.820 --> 36:39.420
there can't be such a person.

36:46.820 --> 36:48.340
Didn't you write a divorce paper

36:48.340 --> 36:49.490
for Yuanji?

36:49.970 --> 36:51.340
Before you go to the Northern Border,

36:51.340 --> 36:52.650
write me one too, will you?

36:52.650 --> 36:54.420
Aren't you not in a hurry to leave?

36:54.420 --> 36:56.150
Why do you need a divorce paper?

36:56.300 --> 36:57.220
Stop pretending.

36:57.220 --> 36:58.090
I saw your discarded draft

36:58.090 --> 36:59.220
on the desk that day.

36:59.900 --> 37:01.570
Just be a good person to the end.

37:01.570 --> 37:03.230
Who told you I'm a good person?

37:04.490 --> 37:06.010
Didn't you say earlier

37:06.340 --> 37:08.300
that I would laugh at you
from the bottom of my heart?

37:08.300 --> 37:09.830
How could I be a good person?

37:31.490 --> 37:34.050
[Honglu Temple]

37:32.950 --> 37:33.780
Mulian Yu,

37:34.450 --> 37:36.250
you attempted to assassinate me

37:36.490 --> 37:38.170
and committed rebellion
against the throne.

37:38.170 --> 37:41.370
According to the law,
your nine clans should be executed!

37:48.090 --> 37:50.820
But I am willing
to spare you the death penalty,

37:51.560 --> 37:54.440
because you are
the right-hand man of Northern Qin.

37:55.530 --> 37:56.940
Our territory

37:57.610 --> 37:58.740
still needs

37:58.740 --> 38:01.450
a blood-stained sword like you
to guard it.

38:03.220 --> 38:05.750
Thank you, Your Majesty,
for sparing my life.

38:10.780 --> 38:12.340
Recorded in this roster

38:13.050 --> 38:16.310
are the unextinguished hidden forces
of our Northern Qin.

38:16.610 --> 38:18.820
Now I'm entrusting it to you.

38:20.400 --> 38:21.810
And Xie Huaigui.

38:23.050 --> 38:25.850
His obsession with avenging
the An and Lu families

38:26.380 --> 38:28.650
is the sharpest blade
for stirring up turmoil in Jiankang

38:28.650 --> 38:31.510
and hindering
Southern Ye's northern expedition.

38:32.780 --> 38:33.900
You should know

38:34.170 --> 38:35.220
how to use him.

38:35.380 --> 38:36.310
Your Majesty, I,

38:37.220 --> 38:39.050
with all due respect,
would like to ask one more thing.

38:39.050 --> 38:42.170
Regarding the case of the Right King of Virtue
conspiring with the enemy and committing treason,

38:42.170 --> 38:44.230
was the evidence truly irrefutable,

38:44.260 --> 38:46.520
or was it a grand miscarriage of justice?

38:53.970 --> 38:55.650
Of course it was a miscarriage of justice.

38:55.650 --> 38:57.090
Otherwise, why would Mulian Ying

38:57.090 --> 38:59.010
hate me to the core?

39:00.020 --> 39:01.810
It was me who personally presented

39:01.810 --> 39:04.770
this vicious scheme to the late Emperor.

39:06.900 --> 39:08.300
And it was me

39:10.340 --> 39:12.540
who wiped out the entire Mulian family.

39:32.160 --> 39:37.300
♪ The past is dust,
we're passing through ♪

39:38.230 --> 39:43.810
♪ No regrets for what we've lost and won ♪

39:44.470 --> 39:50.770
♪ The shape of time begins to fade ♪

39:51.040 --> 39:57.520
♪ Half by choice, half washed away ♪

39:58.030 --> 40:03.450
♪ If fate is fragile,
what is right or wrong ♪

40:04.050 --> 40:09.420
♪ We only live for what we can't let go ♪

40:10.220 --> 40:13.870
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

40:13.970 --> 40:16.420
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

40:16.650 --> 40:22.670
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪

40:21.530 --> 40:22.940
Memorial on the Beifu Reform.

40:22.940 --> 40:26.500
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

40:24.570 --> 40:26.520
After deliberation by the ministers
of the Commandant of Justice,

40:26.520 --> 40:29.490
♪ The heart's a cage,
but peace will break the chains ♪

40:27.090 --> 40:29.520
the Regent requests
His Majesty's review and approval.

40:29.520 --> 40:34.990
♪ No need to speak,
just leave it all to fate ♪

40:29.530 --> 40:31.650
The "Memorial on the Beifu Reform"
submitted by

40:31.650 --> 40:33.570
Xiao Wuyi,
the Grand General of Beifu, is excellent.

40:33.570 --> 40:34.940
It has received His Majesty's approval.

40:34.940 --> 40:37.900
Xiao Wuyi,
Grand General of Beifu, is appointed

40:37.970 --> 40:39.970
Commander-in-Chief of the Six Prefectures.

40:39.970 --> 40:41.940
He shall oversee all military
and administrative affairs of Beifu

40:41.940 --> 40:43.870
under the authority of the Regent.

40:44.170 --> 40:46.490
He shall urge the various prefectures
to provide troops, horses,

40:46.490 --> 40:48.300
provisions, and supplies without delay,

40:48.300 --> 40:49.570
with all matters to be coordinated
under one command.

40:49.260 --> 40:54.680
♪ If fate is fragile,
what is right or wrong ♪

40:50.420 --> 40:54.380
Xiao Wuyi shall immediately lead his troops
back to the Northern Border.

40:54.380 --> 40:56.650
Xiao Yao is appointed
Director of Waterways

40:55.280 --> 41:00.650
♪ We only live for what we can't let go ♪

40:56.940 --> 41:00.300
and shall oversee all matters concerning the repair
of military supply routes and provisions.

41:00.300 --> 41:01.820
Thus decreed.

41:01.450 --> 41:05.100
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

41:02.050 --> 41:04.170
Thank you, Your Highness.

41:05.200 --> 41:07.650
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

41:07.850 --> 41:13.870
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪
